{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle organic facial scrub to effectively cleanse and remove dead skin cells, leaving the skin soft and refreshed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with o\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003erganic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic wheat germ oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of camomile (antiseptic), rose hip (anti-inflammatory) and marigold (regenerating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into dry and clean skin. Moisten fingertips with warm water and massage again till the scrub turns into a white creamy texture. Rinse off with lukewarm water. Use 1-2 times per week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Aqua*, Xanthan Gum*, Kaolin*, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Anisate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Rosa Canina Fruit Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (92,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901084832071,"sku":null,"price":37.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml-749873.jpg?v=1739897173","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}